  • Exception Summary
    Exception
    Description
    IllegalAccessException
    Is thrown when a user tries to access a page he is not entitled to visit.
    IllegalUserFlowException
    Gets thrown when a user accesses a page that can only be accessed through a specific link/user flow directly over the URL.
